  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6992 sitting just below the massive 7000 gamma wall (+17.1B), dealers are likely selling into this rally strength to hedge their long gamma positions. The PIN regime with such heavy positive gamma concentration creates a magnetic effect around 7000, where dealers will aggressively sell any push above this level. Watch for continued selling pressure into 7000-7025 zone, while any dip toward 6975 support should see dealer buying kick in.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to get pinned around 7000 with limited upside breakout potential.",
